{"title": "Pamela, or Virtue Rewarded", "description": "\"Now first published in order to cultivate the Principles of Virtue and Religion in the Minds of the Youth of Both Sexes.<br>A Narrative which has its Foundation in Truth and Nature; and at the same time that it agreeably entertains, by a Variety of curious and affecting Incidents, is intirely divested of all those Images, which, in too many Pieces calculated for Amusement only, tend to inflame the Minds they should instruct.\"(From the frontispiece of the first edition)<br>Pamela tells the story of a 14 year old lady's maid named Pamela whose master, Mr. B., makes unwanted advances towards her. She rejects him continually. In Pamela's letters to her \"poor but exemplary parents\" the story unfolds and we learn her fate. (summary by Annise)\n", "duration": 79834, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "3579", "name": "Samuel Richardson"}], "coverArt": "https://www.archive.org/download/LibrivoxCdCovers3/Pamela_1009.jpg", "copyright_year": "1740", "genres": ["Epistolary Fiction"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "LibriVox Volunteers"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Annise"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Annise"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "mim@can (1949-2017)"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "01", "readers": [1502], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/pamela_0910_librivox/pamela_01_richardson_64kb.mp3", "duration": 2208}, {"section": 2, "title": "02", "readers": [1502], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/pamela_0910_librivox/pamela_02_richardson_64kb.mp3", "duration": 2555}, {"section": 3, "title": "03", "readers": [3157], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/pamela_0910_librivox/pamela_03_richardson_64kb.mp3", "duration": 2193}, {"section": 4, "title": "04", "readers": [3587], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/pamela_0910_librivox/pamela_04_richardson_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1977}, {"section": 5, "title": "05", "readers": [3157], "path": "